text:
Ah. Prosecco. People, you are wasting your time and money going anywhere else. This is a true and very authentic Italian restaurant where the food is high QUALITY and from the very best ingredients. The calamari, wonderful. The service, excellent. We have had the lasagne ( correct spelling), pizza, tiramisu, an amazing special dish with shrimp from the Mediterranean,  the other night a bottle of Chianti from Tuscany that made me swoon and of course, Giuseppe the friendly owner takes pride in welcoming everybody. Must go. Must.
]
Just read a review where they say it takes too long. PEOPLE SLOW DOWN!!! This is how it is done outside the worker bee fast paced USA where people rush to eat and simply gobble down their food and sprint out. This is a place to kick back, laugh, socialize, linger over drinks and dining with friends and family. The idea is to slow you down and RELAX you. Do not miss the whole point. It is not Chili's or Outback. This is an Italian RESTAURANT, an experience. Just breathe and enjoy the wonderful flavors, atmosphere and good company of your dining partner/s.
